      "title": "8 Sri Lankans rescued by Indian Navy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four days ago, 8 persons with a two-and-a-half-month-old baby were dropped on the third sandbar of the Indian sea, and yesterday (21) morning, the Indian Coast Guard rescued all 8 persons.",
        "All 8 boats belonging to two families have been rescued by the Indian Coast Guard and handed over to the Marine Police.",
        "The said 8 are reported to be from Greater Jaffna and Kilinochchi area. (a)"
